    <item>
      <title>“代币化对冲基金”以 37% 的收益率赚得数十亿加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ethena-s-tokenized-hedge-fund-usde-rakes-in-crypto-billions-with-37-yield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旨在复制常见对冲基金交易的加密代币正在吸引价值数十亿美元的投资并在市场上引起广泛关注。然而，这个名为 Ethena 的项目也引发了对其目前约 37% 收益率可持续性的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/ethena-s-tokenized-hedge-fund-usde-rakes-in-crypto-billions-with-37-yield</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Synopsys 因收购 30 亿美元单位而被私募股权公司起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/synopsys-sued-by-pe-firm-for-shopping-3-billion-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州一家私募股权公司起诉新思科技 (Synopsys)，称其在今年早些时候广泛收购其价值 30 亿美元的软件完整性业务时违反了排他性协议，这是私人交易谈判蔓延至法院的罕见案例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/synopsys-sued-by-pe-firm-for-shopping-3-billion-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
